-- Concrete Knowledge Pack — first implementation of the Trade
-- Knowledge Engine. Every entry is trade-agnostic in shape; only
-- the CONTENT is concrete-specific. The exact same structure is
-- used by future packs (bricklaying, plumbing, electrical, etc).
--
-- Sources: gov.uk (Approved Docs), planningportal.co.uk,
-- Mineral Products Association (mineralproducts.org), Concrete
-- Society technical notes, NHBC standards, BS EN 206 + BS 8500
-- summaries, and manufacturer datasheets (Hanson, Tarmac).
--
-- Every entry ships with confidence_score 0.90-1.00 for the
-- seeded set. Lower confidence entries flow through the
-- community contribution pipeline for admin verification.

